@28006  = ~Wait - what is <CHARNAME> doing here?? I just saw you...~
@28007  = ~Calm down, man. Tell us what news is so urgent, and what is confusing you.~ // belt
@28008  = ~Alright, sir. I rushed here to find Lord Entar, to tell you that someone has confessed to the attack on your person, that, um, killed you. Temporarily, I suppose. But still.~
